latestPosts.caption:
met my all time favourite @shraddhakapoor 🥹😭❤️❤️ (still screaming internally aaaahhh)

A lot of you who’s been here for a while might know that I have been a huge fan m of Shraddha Kapoor for years!!! I just love the way she is and relate to her on so many different levels. For years, I have dreamt of meeting her one day and telling her how she’s always been this amazing person to look upto. And guess what, THAT FINALLY HAPPENED YESTERDAY!!!😭❤️

And she was the sweetest person ever, just like I imagined her to be. I told her all that I wanted and she patiently listened to everything and was just the best!! So overwhelmed and happy!! Hence, the long post❤️❤️

p.s: will post outfit pictures from this night later👀🤭

#shraddhakapoor #happypost #awardsnight
